## For Others

Have some other superpowers? No worries, just join our Discord and see how you can help!

## For Designers

Save a copy of our [Figma Design System](https://www.figma.com/file/XITWUHZHNJsIbcCsBkOHpZ/Athens-Design-System?node-id=0%3A1) and begin building off of it!

## For Developers

Don't expect to contribute code on Day 1 if you don't have Clojure experience. But don't worry, you aren't alone!

### Resources
- Learn Clojure
  - read [Onboarding for New Clojurians](https://www.notion.so/athensresearch/Onboarding-for-New-Clojurians-b34b38f30902448cae68afffa02425c1)
  - apply to [ClojureFam](https://github.com/athensresearch/ClojureFam)
  - read [Roam vs Athens Tech Stack](https://www.notion.so/athensresearch/Roam-vs-Athens-Tech-Stack-5318102dcce74f6ab18adfc4d5250e3f)
- Learn Datascript
  - [Datascript Explorer](https://athensresearch.github.io/athens/cards.html#!/athens.devcards.db_boxes)
